Genetic Algorithms, Neural Networks. 

Genetic Algorithms: The paper proposes a classification of the encoding strategies used in genetic algorithms for neural network optimization. It also gives a critical analysis of the current state of development in this field. 

Neural Networks: The paper discusses the application of genetic algorithms to the optimization of artificial neural networks. It also mentions the metaphor of the evolution of the human brain as inspiration for this approach. The paper analyzes the different techniques used to encode neural networks for genetic algorithms.
